nodes.text: Eugene Byrd (born August 28, 1975) is an American actor and producer who has worked on several Hollywood films including Dead Man, Demon Island, Sleepers, and Confess. He appeared in FOX's Bones in seasons 4-9 as Dr. Clark Edison. He did voice work for Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens and is the voice actor of Zander Freemaker, one of the four main protagonists of LEGO Star Wars: The Freemaker Adventures.
